WEBVTT

00:00:03.370 --> 00:00:05.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Nene Iwamizawa.</b></Default>

00:00:05.450 --> 00:00:07.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A junior
in international education.</b></Default>

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Active as a model
in her hometown in Hokkaido</b></Default>

00:00:10.369 --> 00:00:11.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>starting from high school.</b></Default>

00:00:12.160 --> 00:00:14.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Moved to Tokyo
upon entering university.</b></Default>

00:00:14.869 --> 00:00:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Joined a modeling agency</b></Default>

00:00:16.199 --> 00:00:18.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after winning
the Miss Campus contest.</b></Default>

00:00:18.829 --> 00:00:21.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The last time she posted
was in April of this year.</b></Default>

00:00:22.039 --> 00:00:25.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I assume that's around the time
she got puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:00:25.370 --> 00:00:27.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and couldn't
be recognized anymore.</b></Default>

00:00:27.829 --> 00:00:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NENE IWAMIZAWA / TOUKO KIRISHIMA</b></Default>

00:00:30.160 --> 00:00:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But there's still nothing</b></Default>

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:33.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>connecting her
to Touko Kirishima</b></Default>

00:00:34.369 --> 00:00:35.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

00:00:37.079 --> 00:00:38.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Sakuta. Welcome back.</b></Default>

00:00:39.119 --> 00:00:40.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You were out late.</b></Default>

00:00:40.619 --> 00:00:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah. Good to be home.</b></Default>

00:00:42.539 --> 00:00:44.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was doing
a little bit of research.</b></Default>

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Heading off to work?</b></Default>

00:00:45.829 --> 00:00:47.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm getting there early.</b></Default>

00:00:47.159 --> 00:00:50.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm attending a movie festival
in Fukuoka tomorrow.</b></Default>

00:00:50.659 --> 00:00:53.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] The kind you wear
dresses and stuff to?</b></Default>

00:00:53.159 --> 00:00:55.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really want to see that.</b></Default>

00:00:55.250 --> 00:00:58.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you mean photos</b></Default>

00:00:58.250 --> 00:01:00.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, yeah, and about
our hot springs trip.</b></Default>

00:01:00.829 --> 00:01:02.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if you can't make it</b></Default>

00:01:02.329 --> 00:01:04.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ryoko said she'll spend
the night with me</b></Default>

00:01:04.700 --> 00:01:06.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so you don't
have to worry about it.</b></Default>

00:01:07.120 --> 00:01:08.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later.</b></Default>

00:01:09.829 --> 00:01:13.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Soaking in a hot spring
with Mai. I can't wait.</b></Default>

00:01:14.579 --> 00:01:16.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it would be a huge weight
off my shoulders</b></Default>

00:01:17.040 --> 00:01:19.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if things could get
cleared up by Christmas.</b></Default>

00:01:20.659 --> 00:01:22.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ opening theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:02:28.699 --> 00:02:34.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:02:50.039 --> 00:02:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}DECEMBER 16TH</b></Default>

00:02:52.659 --> 00:02:53.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[MAN 1] Goodbye, sir.</b></Default>

00:02:54.120 --> 00:02:55.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}[MAN 2] Have a good one.</b></Default>

00:02:56.039 --> 00:02:57.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}HOLY NIGHT</b></Default>

00:02:57.370 --> 00:02:59.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Then I'll be
leaving now as well.</b></Default>

00:02:59.250 --> 00:03:00.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}Thanks for today.</b></Default>

00:03:02.909 --> 00:03:04.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Azusagawa.</b></Default>

00:03:05.250 --> 00:03:06.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong, Yoshiwa?</b></Default>

00:03:07.409 --> 00:03:10.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's something
I'd like to consult you about.</b></Default>

00:03:11.199 --> 00:03:12.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I had this dream.</b></Default>

00:03:12.949 --> 00:03:14.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>One where someone I know</b></Default>

00:03:14.289 --> 00:03:16.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>asked out the person
he was in love with</b></Default>

00:03:16.449 --> 00:03:17.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and gets rejected.</b></Default>

00:03:17.750 --> 00:03:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] I mean</b></Default>

00:03:20.659 --> 00:03:21.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah.</b></Default>

00:03:22.039 --> 00:03:25.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So in times like this</b></Default>

00:03:25.330 --> 00:03:26.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let me guess.</b></Default>

00:03:26.449 --> 00:03:28.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is about
Yamada and Himeji, right?</b></Default>

00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:29.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:03:30.580 --> 00:03:33.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Well, Yamada isn't
exactly difficult to read</b></Default>

00:03:33.699 --> 00:03:36.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but, I mean, isn't that kind of
a good thing for you?</b></Default>

00:03:36.620 --> 00:03:38.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YOSHIWA] Of course
it's not a good thing.</b></Default>

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:40.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone I like
is being toyed with</b></Default>

00:03:40.750 --> 00:03:42.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by such a repulsive girl.</b></Default>

00:03:42.409 --> 00:03:44.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you really
want to put an end to that</b></Default>

00:03:44.539 --> 00:03:46.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why don't you
just grab Yamada's attention?</b></Default>

00:03:46.830 --> 00:03:47.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how?</b></Default>

00:03:47.949 --> 00:03:50.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's just no way
that I can win against Himeji.</b></Default>

00:03:51.199 --> 00:03:54.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd like you to listen to me
without getting angry, okay?</b></Default>

00:03:54.539 --> 00:03:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I recall correctly</b></Default>

00:03:56.949 --> 00:03:59.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for a beach volleyball match
starting tomorrow, right?</b></Default>

00:03:59.750 --> 00:04:01.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, yeah, I am.</b></Default>

00:04:01.330 --> 00:04:04.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A guy like Yamada
would definitely fall for you</b></Default>

00:04:04.120 --> 00:04:06.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just by sneaking peeks
of your swimsuit tan lines.</b></Default>

00:04:08.699 --> 00:04:10.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you really think so?</b></Default>

00:04:14.409 --> 00:04:16.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[indistinct announcement]</b></Default>

00:04:16.500 --> 00:04:18.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:04:18.120 --> 00:04:20.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A whole lot of people
want to talk to me today.</b></Default>

00:04:20.790 --> 00:04:23.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise I'm not coming to you
for advice, okay?</b></Default>

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:24.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:04:25.500 --> 00:04:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I figured I should apologize
about yesterday.</b></Default>

00:04:28.079 --> 00:04:30.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:04:31.449 --> 00:04:34.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My sudden outburst
was very rude, so I'm sorry.</b></Default>

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, do you have
some free time now?</b></Default>

00:04:38.699 --> 00:04:42.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know, Himeji, you really are
quite adept academically.</b></Default>

00:04:42.410 --> 00:04:45.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you should
have a teacher looking after you</b></Default>

00:04:45.079 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who's more fit for your level.</b></Default>

00:04:46.750 --> 00:04:48.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you feel
so strongly about it</b></Default>

00:04:48.540 --> 00:04:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why don't you level up to be
more suitable for me?</b></Default>

00:04:51.329 --> 00:04:53.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not so sure
that I can level up</b></Default>

00:04:53.500 --> 00:04:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>any further at this point.</b></Default>

00:04:55.290 --> 00:04:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any particular
university you want to go to?</b></Default>

00:04:58.199 --> 00:04:59.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, not right now.</b></Default>

00:04:59.949 --> 00:05:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the university
you're attending?</b></Default>

00:05:04.329 --> 00:05:07.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So my girlfriend and I could
have a fun campus life together.</b></Default>

00:05:08.079 --> 00:05:10.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You shouldn't go telling
such an impure motive</b></Default>

00:05:10.449 --> 00:05:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so shamelessly
to your student, you know?</b></Default>

00:05:12.829 --> 00:05:14.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't you have
any other reasons?</b></Default>

00:05:15.040 --> 00:05:16.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, let's see.</b></Default>

00:05:16.790 --> 00:05:19.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It wasn't my plan when I was
taking entrance exams</b></Default>

00:05:19.790 --> 00:05:22.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but now I'm working towards
acquiring a teacher's license.</b></Default>

00:05:22.790 --> 00:05:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, you're really going to
become a teacher, Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:05:25.829 --> 00:05:27.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll get
the credentials at least.</b></Default>

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:30.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I haven't told anybody this</b></Default>

00:05:30.250 --> 00:05:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so keep it a secret
for me, okay?</b></Default>

00:05:32.079 --> 00:05:34.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't even
told your girlfriend yet?</b></Default>

00:05:34.290 --> 00:05:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-No, I haven't.
-Not even Miss Futaba?</b></Default>

00:05:36.370 --> 00:05:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nope. Not even her.</b></Default>

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:41.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay, then it'll be
our little secret</b></Default>

00:05:41.540 --> 00:05:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just between you and me.</b></Default>

00:05:44.500 --> 00:05:46.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyway, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:05:46.370 --> 00:05:48.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how's your homework assignment
coming along?</b></Default>

00:05:48.660 --> 00:05:49.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Figure it out yet?</b></Default>

00:05:49.910 --> 00:05:51.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Absolutely no clue.</b></Default>

00:05:53.250 --> 00:05:55.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps it's better
that way, though.</b></Default>

00:05:55.199 --> 00:05:56.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

00:05:56.500 --> 00:05:57.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And if I think about it</b></Default>

00:05:58.000 --> 00:05:59.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's probably better
for you, too</b></Default>

00:05:59.870 --> 00:06:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you don't fix
my puberty syndrome.</b></Default>

00:06:02.000 --> 00:06:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you mean by that?</b></Default>

00:06:03.579 --> 00:06:06.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I looked it up, I learned
that it's called clairvoyance.</b></Default>

00:06:06.750 --> 00:06:07.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Clairvoyance?</b></Default>

00:06:08.040 --> 00:06:11.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right. No matter
how far away someone may be</b></Default>

00:06:11.290 --> 00:06:13.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what they're doing
or where they are</b></Default>

00:06:13.290 --> 00:06:15.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can see through their eyes
and know their thoughts.</b></Default>

00:06:16.040 --> 00:06:19.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's why I know a whole
lot of your secrets as well.</b></Default>

00:06:19.750 --> 00:06:22.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like how you're trying
to find Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:06:22.449 --> 00:06:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:06:24.620 --> 00:06:25.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you surprised?</b></Default>

00:06:25.790 --> 00:06:27.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If that's true, Himeji</b></Default>

00:06:27.370 --> 00:06:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you know
where Touko Kirishima is</b></Default>

00:06:29.329 --> 00:06:30.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and what she's doing right now?</b></Default>

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:32.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry, but that I don't know.</b></Default>

00:06:33.040 --> 00:06:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The thing is, I only see
people I've met, and...</b></Default>

00:06:36.370 --> 00:06:37.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[claps]</b></Default>

00:06:37.449 --> 00:06:38.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>...someone that I've had</b></Default>

00:06:38.790 --> 00:06:41.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a relatively strong collision
with in person.</b></Default>

00:06:44.750 --> 00:06:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So that's it.
Quantum entanglement.</b></Default>

00:06:47.579 --> 00:06:49.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, I can help you out</b></Default>

00:06:49.160 --> 00:06:51.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you just let me
meet Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:06:51.910 --> 00:06:53.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then I can
read her mind for you.</b></Default>

00:06:53.910 --> 00:06:56.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hold on, Himeji. You were able
to see Touko Kirishima?</b></Default>

00:06:56.870 --> 00:06:57.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I saw her.</b></Default>

00:06:58.040 --> 00:07:00.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's the girl dressed as
a miniskirt Santa Claus, right?</b></Default>

00:07:00.949 --> 00:07:03.199 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The other day</b></Default>

00:07:03.290 --> 00:07:04.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with her livestream coming up.</b></Default>

00:07:05.500 --> 00:07:07.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But knowing that information</b></Default>

00:07:07.660 --> 00:07:09.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the dream makes more sense now.</b></Default>

00:07:09.410 --> 00:07:12.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And we know why we were
together on Christmas Eve.</b></Default>

00:07:14.660 --> 00:07:15.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Himeji</b></Default>

00:07:15.829 --> 00:07:18.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are you free to hang out
on the 24th?</b></Default>

00:07:18.079 --> 00:07:20.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're insisting
that I must, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:07:20.790 --> 00:07:23.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't be opposed
to going on a date.</b></Default>

00:07:24.540 --> 00:07:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Things are
starting to get strange.</b></Default>

00:07:27.449 --> 00:07:28.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But</b></Default>

00:07:28.699 --> 00:07:31.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if what's causing this is really
quantum entanglement</b></Default>

00:07:33.410 --> 00:07:36.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>wouldn't I be able to see
through her eyes as well?</b></Default>

00:07:37.160 --> 00:07:38.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inhales]</b></Default>

00:07:39.329 --> 00:07:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[exhales]</b></Default>

00:07:44.449 --> 00:07:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[pop song playing]</b></Default>

00:07:45.829 --> 00:07:46.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[soft gasp]</b></Default>

00:07:53.660 --> 00:07:56.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RECOMMENDED WINTER OUTFITS</b></Default>

00:07:59.040 --> 00:08:00.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Oh, this one's cute.</b></Default>

00:08:00.790 --> 00:08:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder if Mr. Sakuta
likes stuff like this.</b></Default>

00:08:03.910 --> 00:08:06.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have to pick
where we're going, too.</b></Default>

00:08:06.370 --> 00:08:08.699 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're ending up
at his university at the end</b></Default>

00:08:08.790 --> 00:08:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I guess it'll be Kamakura
on the way.</b></Default>

00:08:11.370 --> 00:08:13.949 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Sara, the water's ready.
Go take your bath.</b></Default>

00:08:14.040 --> 00:08:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Okay.</b></Default>

00:08:21.329 --> 00:08:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KAEDE] {\i1}Big Brother</b></Default>

00:08:24.370 --> 00:08:25.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:08:27.160 --> 00:08:29.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see now.
So that's how it works.</b></Default>

00:08:29.660 --> 00:08:31.449 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you
gonna do, Big Brother?</b></Default>

00:08:31.579 --> 00:08:34.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell her I'm in the bath
and that I'll call her back.</b></Default>

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

00:08:36.409 --> 00:08:38.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really hope
she'll forgive me for this</b></Default>

00:08:38.539 --> 00:08:41.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and let me push our hot spring
sleepover to a later day.</b></Default>

00:08:43.289 --> 00:08:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>DECEMBER 24TH</b></Default>

00:08:50.370 --> 00:08:51.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SANTA] Merry Christmas.</b></Default>

00:08:52.620 --> 00:08:53.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Merry Christmas.</b></Default>

00:08:53.870 --> 00:08:55.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}It's just{\i0}
{\i1}like the dream.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:08:55.750 --> 00:08:57.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SANTA] Merry Christmas.
Thank you.</b></Default>

00:08:57.659 --> 00:08:59.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WOMAN] Sorry for the wait.</b></Default>

00:09:00.200 --> 00:09:01.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait. Mai?</b></Default>

00:09:01.500 --> 00:09:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What are you doing here?</b></Default>

00:09:03.080 --> 00:09:04.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm tagging along on your date.</b></Default>

00:09:04.870 --> 00:09:06.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, Mai, when I
explained the situation</b></Default>

00:09:07.039 --> 00:09:09.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>over the phone the other day</b></Default>

00:09:09.700 --> 00:09:12.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, and that's why
I came all prepared like this.</b></Default>

00:09:12.830 --> 00:09:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, um, Mr. Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:09:16.500 --> 00:09:18.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is the meaning of this?</b></Default>

00:09:18.120 --> 00:09:20.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sorry, uh</b></Default>

00:09:20.830 --> 00:09:22.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you mind coming with me?</b></Default>

00:09:22.580 --> 00:09:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My car is parked
right over there.</b></Default>

00:09:30.039 --> 00:09:32.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it okay if I call you Sara?</b></Default>

00:09:32.080 --> 00:09:34.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, yeah. That's okay with me.</b></Default>

00:09:34.200 --> 00:09:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can go ahead
and call me Mai if you want.</b></Default>

00:09:36.750 --> 00:09:37.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sure.</b></Default>

00:09:37.909 --> 00:09:40.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is Sakuta teaching you properly
at the cram school?</b></Default>

00:09:40.830 --> 00:09:43.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I have a surprising
following for my students.</b></Default>

00:09:43.750 --> 00:09:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wasn't asking you, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:09:45.659 --> 00:09:49.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do think he has a surprising
following from his students.</b></Default>

00:09:49.159 --> 00:09:50.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, really?</b></Default>

00:09:50.159 --> 00:09:51.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aside from myself</b></Default>

00:09:51.620 --> 00:09:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he has Yamada and Yoshiwa
as cram school students as well.</b></Default>

00:09:54.789 --> 00:09:57.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Both of them have approached him
for relationship advice.</b></Default>

00:09:57.909 --> 00:10:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta, what exactly
are you teaching?</b></Default>

00:10:01.200 --> 00:10:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yoshiwa happens to be
a beach volleyball player</b></Default>

00:10:03.830 --> 00:10:05.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but she's really quite subdued</b></Default>

00:10:05.580 --> 00:10:08.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and she's in love
with an oblivious boy.</b></Default>

00:10:08.120 --> 00:10:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, apparently that boy
is actually in love with me.</b></Default>

00:10:11.450 --> 00:10:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So to help things along</b></Default>

00:10:13.370 --> 00:10:15.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta gave her
some unbelievable advice</b></Default>

00:10:15.789 --> 00:10:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for him to look her way.</b></Default>

00:10:17.080 --> 00:10:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Knowing him, I'm sure he said</b></Default>

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>"Let him sneak a peek
at your swimsuit tan lines."</b></Default>

00:10:21.870 --> 00:10:23.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Amazing. That's exactly right.</b></Default>

00:10:23.870 --> 00:10:25.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gotta hand it to Mai.</b></Default>

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:26.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She knows me better than anyone.</b></Default>

00:10:27.000 --> 00:10:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's something
Sakuta is likely to say.</b></Default>

00:10:31.700 --> 00:10:34.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you two really are
an actual couple, aren't you?</b></Default>

00:10:34.870 --> 00:10:36.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did you think that was a lie?</b></Default>

00:10:36.750 --> 00:10:39.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, no, not at all.</b></Default>

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:41.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just meant you two
get along really well</b></Default>

00:10:41.750 --> 00:10:44.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Mr. Sakuta is making faces
he doesn't show at cram school.</b></Default>

00:10:45.039 --> 00:10:45.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am?</b></Default>

00:10:46.039 --> 00:10:47.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, it's true.</b></Default>

00:10:47.250 --> 00:10:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta really does love me
quite a lot.</b></Default>

00:10:55.700 --> 00:10:57.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, Mai, where are we going?</b></Default>

00:10:57.450 --> 00:11:00.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought we could pick up some
souvenirs for Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:11:04.039 --> 00:11:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get it now.</b></Default>

00:11:05.789 --> 00:11:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We get her distracted with
the Mont Blanc, and then bam!</b></Default>

00:11:09.370 --> 00:11:11.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where do you need
to hit her exactly?</b></Default>

00:11:11.909 --> 00:11:13.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think anywhere should be fine.</b></Default>

00:11:13.659 --> 00:11:16.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] Then this shouldn't be
too difficult to pull off.</b></Default>

00:11:16.580 --> 00:11:18.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You go wait in line, Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:11:18.409 --> 00:11:21.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I need to buy some sweets that
Nodoka asked me to pick up.</b></Default>

00:11:21.870 --> 00:11:23.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'll take Sara
along with me.</b></Default>

00:11:23.750 --> 00:11:24.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[BOTH] Huh?</b></Default>

00:11:29.000 --> 00:11:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\an8}RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF SANTA CLAUS</b></Default>

00:11:32.370 --> 00:11:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckling]</b></Default>

00:11:33.909 --> 00:11:36.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA]I wonder
if Himeji is all right.</b></Default>

00:11:36.370 --> 00:11:39.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Suppose taking a little peek
won't hurt.</b></Default>

00:11:45.370 --> 00:11:48.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA]{\i1} What in the world{\i0}
{\i1}am I even doing?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:49.330 --> 00:11:52.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I was supposed to be{\i0}
{\i1}on a date with Mr. Sakuta.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:52.909 --> 00:11:55.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I was going to rent a kimono{\i0}
{\i1}at Komachi Street{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:55.789 --> 00:11:57.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and make him tell me I'm cute.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:11:57.830 --> 00:12:00.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Then he was gonna choose{\i0}
{\i1}an accessory for me</b></Default>

00:12:00.370 --> 00:12:02.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and we'd have tea{\i0}
{\i1}at the bamboo temple.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:03.659 --> 00:12:05.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}All of it has been ruined.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:05.539 --> 00:12:06.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}At this rate</b></Default>

00:12:06.659 --> 00:12:08.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}he won't look my way at all{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:09.500 --> 00:12:11.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}because she's here.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:12.750 --> 00:12:16.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Why does someone like her{\i0}
{\i1}have to be dating Mr. Sakuta?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:17.909 --> 00:12:20.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, can I ask one thing?</b></Default>

00:12:20.659 --> 00:12:22.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] It doesn't
have to be one thing.</b></Default>

00:12:23.659 --> 00:12:25.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Why are you
with Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:12:26.120 --> 00:12:28.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think you guys
are in the same league.</b></Default>

00:12:29.289 --> 00:12:32.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you saying I'm not suitable
to be Mr. Sakuta's girlfriend?</b></Default>

00:12:33.830 --> 00:12:35.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The opposite.</b></Default>

00:12:35.289 --> 00:12:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean, you're able to date</b></Default>

00:12:36.830 --> 00:12:39.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>much more handsome actors
or popular idols, right, Mai?</b></Default>

00:12:40.250 --> 00:12:42.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What would I do dating them?</b></Default>

00:12:42.330 --> 00:12:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}Huh?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:43.330 --> 00:12:45.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}What does she mean by that?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:12:45.580 --> 00:12:47.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would I brag about it
to my friends?</b></Default>

00:12:47.750 --> 00:12:50.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, yeah</b></Default>

00:12:50.409 --> 00:12:51.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I mean</b></Default>

00:12:52.159 --> 00:12:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is that bad?</b></Default>

00:12:53.289 --> 00:12:54.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't think so.</b></Default>

00:12:54.409 --> 00:12:56.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you're proud
of your significant other</b></Default>

00:12:56.620 --> 00:12:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what's the harm
in bragging a bit?</b></Default>

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps the one who thinks
that isn't a good thing is you.</b></Default>

00:13:03.080 --> 00:13:05.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}No, that isn't true.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:05.370 --> 00:13:06.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That's not...{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:06.500 --> 00:13:09.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sara, why did you
choose Mr. Sakuta?</b></Default>

00:13:09.950 --> 00:13:10.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Because--</b></Default>

00:13:11.039 --> 00:13:13.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it that you thought
you'd tease him a bit</b></Default>

00:13:13.330 --> 00:13:15.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because he's
Mai Sakurajima's boyfriend?</b></Default>

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:18.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, how is that going for you?</b></Default>

00:13:21.289 --> 00:13:23.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}She really is pretty.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:24.539 --> 00:13:25.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}There's nothing I can do{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:25.950 --> 00:13:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}as long as he has{\i0}
{\i1}a girlfriend like her.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:28.080 --> 00:13:29.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So, why did I...{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:30.409 --> 00:13:32.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whenever I laid eyes
on boys in the past</b></Default>

00:13:32.539 --> 00:13:35.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>every one of them ended up
falling in love with me</b></Default>

00:13:35.250 --> 00:13:36.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even the ones with girlfriends.</b></Default>

00:13:37.500 --> 00:13:41.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But as it turns out, I wasn't
one of those girlfriends, was I?</b></Default>

00:13:41.620 --> 00:13:44.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}And Sakuta wasn't{\i0}
{\i1}one of those boys either.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:44.580 --> 00:13:46.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}That's enough of this.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:46.159 --> 00:13:48.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you never really know
for sure.</b></Default>

00:13:48.289 --> 00:13:49.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Just stop.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:49.450 --> 00:13:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Stop it!{\i0}</b></Default>

00:13:50.789 --> 00:13:53.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}If I go any further</b></Default>

00:13:53.330 --> 00:13:55.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry
I derailed the conversation.</b></Default>

00:13:56.000 --> 00:13:57.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You asked before</b></Default>

00:13:57.330 --> 00:14:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>why is it that I chose Sakuta.
Isn't that right?</b></Default>

00:14:00.409 --> 00:14:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

00:14:01.409 --> 00:14:05.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's because Sakuta always
listens to all my selfish whims</b></Default>

00:14:05.330 --> 00:14:07.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even if he complains about them.</b></Default>

00:14:07.500 --> 00:14:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But not only that</b></Default>

00:14:08.830 --> 00:14:10.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he always compliments
my cooking as well.</b></Default>

00:14:11.039 --> 00:14:13.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And he knows how to properly
put his love into words.</b></Default>

00:14:14.700 --> 00:14:17.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA]{\i1} I don't get it.{\i0}
{\i1}I don't get it at all.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are many more reasons.</b></Default>

00:14:19.120 --> 00:14:20.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He cares about his friends.</b></Default>

00:14:20.700 --> 00:14:23.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He thinks dearly about
his cram school students too.</b></Default>

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:26.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}He's someone who can{\i0}
{\i1}give his all for someone else</b></Default>

00:14:27.659 --> 00:14:30.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}all while asserting{\i0}
{\i1}that he's doing it for himself.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:14:31.450 --> 00:14:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did that provide an answer
to your question?</b></Default>

00:14:35.950 --> 00:14:38.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's very difficult
to explain with words</b></Default>

00:14:38.409 --> 00:14:40.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but if you want to know
the purpose for us dating</b></Default>

00:14:41.039 --> 00:14:42.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can tell you that easily.</b></Default>

00:14:43.289 --> 00:14:45.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that purpose?</b></Default>

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:48.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] The reason why
Sakuta and I are dating</b></Default>

00:14:49.830 --> 00:14:52.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is so we can be happy together.</b></Default>

00:14:53.750 --> 00:14:56.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the one person
that makes me feel that way.</b></Default>

00:14:56.539 --> 00:14:58.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So maybe that's why
I chose Sakuta.</b></Default>

00:14:58.870 --> 00:15:00.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}What is this?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:00.409 --> 00:15:02.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}It doesn't make any sense.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:02.580 --> 00:15:06.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, I'd say I'm already
plenty happy right now.</b></Default>

00:15:06.250 --> 00:15:07.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}No. It's impossible.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:07.870 --> 00:15:10.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you think I'm lying</b></Default>

00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:12.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll allow you to read my mind.</b></Default>

00:15:12.909 --> 00:15:15.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That way, I think
you'll understand everything.</b></Default>

00:15:16.080 --> 00:15:17.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}Wait. No, wait.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:17.870 --> 00:15:19.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I don't want to know.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:19.750 --> 00:15:21.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}There's no way{\i0}
{\i1}in the world I can win</b></Default>

00:15:21.750 --> 00:15:23.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}not against someone like this.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:15:23.580 --> 00:15:24.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

00:15:25.620 --> 00:15:27.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't touch me!</b></Default>

00:15:27.830 --> 00:15:28.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:33.909 --> 00:15:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No good.</b></Default>

00:15:35.039 --> 00:15:36.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't connect anymore.</b></Default>

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:38.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, excuse me, sir.</b></Default>

00:15:38.789 --> 00:15:41.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you Azusagawa by any chance?</b></Default>

00:15:41.159 --> 00:15:42.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, yes, I am.</b></Default>

00:15:42.539 --> 00:15:44.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have a call
from a member of your party.</b></Default>

00:15:46.080 --> 00:15:47.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mai?</b></Default>

00:15:47.409 --> 00:15:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] {\i1}I'm sorry</b></Default>

00:15:49.950 --> 00:15:50.909 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

00:15:51.000 --> 00:15:52.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:15:56.330 --> 00:15:58.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[inaudible]</b></Default>

00:15:58.120 --> 00:15:59.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:16:07.120 --> 00:16:08.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where else?</b></Default>

00:16:08.289 --> 00:16:10.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] And we'd have tea
at the bamboo temple.</b></Default>

00:16:12.120 --> 00:16:14.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sakuta! Did you find her?</b></Default>

00:16:14.500 --> 00:16:15.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No luck.</b></Default>

00:16:15.539 --> 00:16:18.159 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry.
I may have said too much.</b></Default>

00:16:18.789 --> 00:16:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Mai</b></Default>

00:16:19.950 --> 00:16:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>do you know
of any bamboo temples?</b></Default>

00:16:28.120 --> 00:16:29.659 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:16:39.200 --> 00:16:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

00:16:43.159 --> 00:16:44.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank goodness.</b></Default>

00:16:44.289 --> 00:16:47.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps] Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:16:48.659 --> 00:16:49.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ow.</b></Default>

00:16:49.620 --> 00:16:50.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

00:16:59.450 --> 00:17:00.409 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But why?</b></Default>

00:17:00.500 --> 00:17:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a teacher.
If one of my students got lost</b></Default>

00:17:02.950 --> 00:17:04.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd search desperately.</b></Default>

00:17:04.329 --> 00:17:05.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not what I mean.</b></Default>

00:17:05.660 --> 00:17:07.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Besides</b></Default>

00:17:07.700 --> 00:17:09.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a plan together.</b></Default>

00:17:09.160 --> 00:17:10.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A plan?</b></Default>

00:17:10.200 --> 00:17:13.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, so you can bump your head
into Touko Kirishima, remember?</b></Default>

00:17:14.250 --> 00:17:16.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll open up
the box of Mont Blancs</b></Default>

00:17:16.160 --> 00:17:18.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and hand it over
to Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:17:18.450 --> 00:17:20.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So when she peers into the box</b></Default>

00:17:20.160 --> 00:17:22.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how about you give her a good
whack right on the noggin?</b></Default>

00:17:23.410 --> 00:17:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's no good.</b></Default>

00:17:25.039 --> 00:17:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm?</b></Default>

00:17:26.039 --> 00:17:28.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't see anything anymore</b></Default>

00:17:28.079 --> 00:17:29.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or hear anything.</b></Default>

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:32.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The voices in Mr. Sakuta's heart</b></Default>

00:17:32.410 --> 00:17:34.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or the voices of anyone else.</b></Default>

00:17:35.250 --> 00:17:37.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why I got scared
and ran away.</b></Default>

00:17:38.329 --> 00:17:40.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I see. You want another bump?</b></Default>

00:17:42.369 --> 00:17:43.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Why?</b></Default>

00:17:46.329 --> 00:17:47.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why?</b></Default>

00:17:48.119 --> 00:17:49.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? [sobs]</b></Default>

00:17:49.750 --> 00:17:51.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why can't I
hear anything anymore?</b></Default>

00:17:51.750 --> 00:17:53.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why is this happening?</b></Default>

00:17:54.369 --> 00:17:55.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be okay.</b></Default>

00:17:55.579 --> 00:17:57.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Being cured
of your puberty syndrome</b></Default>

00:17:57.500 --> 00:17:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-is a good thing.
-No, it isn't good at all!</b></Default>

00:17:59.789 --> 00:18:02.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's gone, it means that I'm
completely useless to you now.</b></Default>

00:18:03.000 --> 00:18:04.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've already helped me a ton</b></Default>

00:18:04.579 --> 00:18:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just by being
one of my students.</b></Default>

00:18:06.329 --> 00:18:09.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna be more than just
another one of your students.</b></Default>

00:18:09.200 --> 00:18:12.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I'm being honest with you</b></Default>

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd prefer
not to have to use you</b></Default>

00:18:15.829 --> 00:18:18.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so I'm actually glad
you've been cured.</b></Default>

00:18:18.450 --> 00:18:20.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really. Thanks for trying.</b></Default>

00:18:21.079 --> 00:18:22.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, though?</b></Default>

00:18:22.289 --> 00:18:24.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can you say that
when you were fully aware</b></Default>

00:18:24.700 --> 00:18:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of what I was doing
with my puberty syndrome?</b></Default>

00:18:27.119 --> 00:18:29.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sobs] I peered
into everyone's hearts</b></Default>

00:18:29.500 --> 00:18:31.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and toyed with their emotions.</b></Default>

00:18:31.200 --> 00:18:33.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know
every bit of that is true.</b></Default>

00:18:33.119 --> 00:18:35.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So why are you
still being so kind to me?</b></Default>

00:18:35.700 --> 00:18:36.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

00:18:36.869 --> 00:18:38.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, that's easy.</b></Default>

00:18:38.200 --> 00:18:40.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's just the kind of person
I want to become.</b></Default>

00:18:41.500 --> 00:18:43.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] Please be
rightfully angry with me.</b></Default>

00:18:43.750 --> 00:18:46.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At least act like
you're troubled a little bit.</b></Default>

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:48.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Because at this point</b></Default>

00:18:48.500 --> 00:18:50.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm totally lost.</b></Default>

00:18:51.079 --> 00:18:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not being fair</b></Default>

00:18:54.660 --> 00:18:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, we adults do tend
to be rather cunning.</b></Default>

00:18:58.539 --> 00:18:59.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

00:19:00.329 --> 00:19:01.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:19:02.660 --> 00:19:03.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>right now</b></Default>

00:19:03.660 --> 00:19:06.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I really, really wish
I had fallen in love with you</b></Default>

00:19:06.369 --> 00:19:08.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in a much more proper way.</b></Default>

00:19:08.950 --> 00:19:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think you know this</b></Default>

00:19:10.289 --> 00:19:13.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the school's manual says
that teachers are prohibited</b></Default>

00:19:13.289 --> 00:19:14.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from dating students.</b></Default>

00:19:15.950 --> 00:19:16.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

00:19:17.000 --> 00:19:19.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, if I get accepted
to my first choice school</b></Default>

00:19:19.660 --> 00:19:21.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll ask you out again
at that time.</b></Default>

00:19:22.079 --> 00:19:24.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That would be more appropriate.</b></Default>

00:19:24.700 --> 00:19:27.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MAI] But you can't</b></Default>

00:19:27.829 --> 00:19:31.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Remember, Touko Kirishima
is waiting at the university.</b></Default>

00:19:34.289 --> 00:19:36.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[pop song playing on phone]</b></Default>

00:19:37.829 --> 00:19:42.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>LIVE</b></Default>

00:19:45.200 --> 00:19:46.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

00:19:49.579 --> 00:19:51.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're late. It's over.</b></Default>

00:19:51.789 --> 00:19:54.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You could have waited
at least a little while for me.</b></Default>

00:19:59.579 --> 00:20:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nene Iwamizawa.</b></Default>

00:20:01.289 --> 00:20:02.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's your name, right?</b></Default>

00:20:02.750 --> 00:20:05.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Junior
in international education</b></Default>

00:20:05.289 --> 00:20:07.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and last year's
Miss Campus winner.</b></Default>

00:20:07.450 --> 00:20:11.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-And you're from Hokkaido--
-My name is Touko Kirishima.</b></Default>

00:20:13.700 --> 00:20:15.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:20:15.200 --> 00:20:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who have you been speaking to
the past few minutes?</b></Default>

00:20:18.750 --> 00:20:20.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is she here right now?</b></Default>

00:20:21.200 --> 00:20:22.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not now.</b></Default>

00:20:22.700 --> 00:20:23.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She just left.</b></Default>

00:20:23.950 --> 00:20:26.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's weird</b></Default>

00:20:26.200 --> 00:20:28.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when I peeked
into your heart before.</b></Default>

00:20:28.160 --> 00:20:31.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but that's likely because
you were seeing what I saw.</b></Default>

00:20:31.910 --> 00:20:34.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh. So in that case</b></Default>

00:20:34.200 --> 00:20:36.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wouldn't have been
of much use to you anyway.</b></Default>

00:20:37.329 --> 00:20:39.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel so stupid.</b></Default>

00:20:40.079 --> 00:20:42.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, at least we didn't
come here with high hopes</b></Default>

00:20:42.700 --> 00:20:44.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it's probably better
this way.</b></Default>

00:20:46.160 --> 00:20:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, I guess that's true.</b></Default>

00:20:48.750 --> 00:20:50.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, phooey.
It's Christmas Eve</b></Default>

00:20:50.789 --> 00:20:52.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but nothing good
is even happening.</b></Default>

00:20:52.869 --> 00:20:55.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How about I buy you a cake
on the way home?</b></Default>

00:20:55.250 --> 00:20:56.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, you mean it?</b></Default>

00:20:56.660 --> 00:20:57.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles] Hooray!</b></Default>

00:21:07.079 --> 00:21:08.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs deeply]</b></Default>

00:21:08.869 --> 00:21:10.289 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens and closes]</b></Default>

00:21:10.619 --> 00:21:12.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How is it? Feels good, huh?</b></Default>

00:21:13.410 --> 00:21:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This place is heavenly.
The only thing better would be</b></Default>

00:21:16.369 --> 00:21:18.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I could take this bath
together with you.</b></Default>

00:21:31.250 --> 00:21:32.789 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That good enough for you?</b></Default>

00:21:33.910 --> 00:21:35.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To be honest, Mai...</b></Default>

00:21:36.160 --> 00:21:37.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hymen ruptured!</b></Default>

00:21:37.250 --> 00:21:40.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll make my yukata wet</b></Default>

00:21:40.329 --> 00:21:41.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, right.</b></Default>

00:21:41.539 --> 00:21:43.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I got a text
from Futaba earlier.</b></Default>

00:21:43.789 --> 00:21:45.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She asked</b></Default>

00:21:45.950 --> 00:21:48.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could I borrow him
for just a minute?"</b></Default>

00:21:48.619 --> 00:21:49.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, what's up?</b></Default>

00:21:49.700 --> 00:21:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIO] {\i1}You really said something{\i0}
{\i1}you shouldn't have to Kasai.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:21:53.289 --> 00:21:54.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? Did something happen?</b></Default>

00:21:55.000 --> 00:21:57.329 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I told him{\i0}
{\i1}that I couldn't date a student</b></Default>

00:21:57.410 --> 00:21:59.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and he responded with</b></Default>

00:22:00.079 --> 00:22:03.079 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}to my first choice university</b></Default>

00:22:03.160 --> 00:22:05.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, he really did it, huh?</b></Default>

00:22:05.369 --> 00:22:07.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That was your suggestion</b></Default>

00:22:07.289 --> 00:22:09.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}So how about{\i0}
{\i1}you take responsibility{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:11.579 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}and help him get accepted{\i0}
{\i1}to his first choice?{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:11.660 --> 00:22:13.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on</b></Default>

00:22:13.539 --> 00:22:14.829 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}That's all I have to say.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:14.910 --> 00:22:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}Please tell Sakurajima{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:16.329 --> 00:22:18.119 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}I'm sorry{\i0}
{\i1}for bothering her on holiday.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:19.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}See ya.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:19.250 --> 00:22:20.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did Futaba have to say?</b></Default>

00:22:21.039 --> 00:22:23.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] That she's sorry
for bothering you</b></Default>

00:22:23.289 --> 00:22:24.619 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>during the holiday.</b></Default>

00:22:25.119 --> 00:22:26.539 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on, you two</b></Default>

00:22:26.619 --> 00:22:28.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>come inside
before you both catch a cold.</b></Default>

00:22:29.039 --> 00:22:30.039 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Okay.</b></Default>

00:22:30.700 --> 00:22:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] Mai.</b></Default>

00:22:32.829 --> 00:22:34.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thanks for today.</b></Default>

00:22:36.539 --> 00:22:38.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're very welcome.</b></Default>

00:22:47.039 --> 00:22:49.369 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SAKUTA] {\i1}That night</b></Default>

00:22:50.369 --> 00:22:53.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>{\i1}A strange dream that I can{\i0}
{\i1}only think was reality.{\i0}</b></Default>

00:22:55.500 --> 00:22:57.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[♪ closing theme song playing]</b></Default>

00:22:57.579 --> 00:23:04.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>RASCAL DOES NOT DREAM
OF HIS STUDENT</b></Default>

00:23:55.789 --> 00:23:58.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SARA] {\i1}Oh, Mr. Sakuta</b></Default>

00:23:58.289 --> 00:23:59.869 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>NEXT EPISODE
#11 THE WORLD DREAMS</b></Default>
